option.name: originalContent
option.value:
<Project> <Target Name="CleanGenerated" BeforeTargets="PreBuildEvent" Condition="Exists('$(ProjectDir)SourceGeneratedViewer')"> <Message Text="Removing SourceGeneratedViewer directory..." Importance="high" /> <RemoveDir Directories="$(ProjectDir)SourceGeneratedViewer"> <OnError ExecuteTargets="" /> </RemoveDir> </Target>
<!-- <PropertyGroup> <EmitCompilerGeneratedFiles>true</EmitCompilerGeneratedFiles> <CompilerGeneratedFilesOutputPath>SourceGeneratedViewer</CompilerGeneratedFilesOutputPath> </PropertyGroup> -->
<ItemGroup> <Compile Remove="SourceGeneratedViewer\**" /> <None Include="SourceGeneratedViewer\**" /> </ItemGroup> </Project>

Importance="high" /> <RemoveDir Directories="$(ProjectDir)SourceGeneratedViewer" ContinueOnError="Warn" /> </Target>
